name: Bretta (Brett’s Wife)
description: Bretta is a long-term, community-driven memecoin project, building a unique narrative as "Brett’s wife," inspired by the Brett on Base phenomenon. Launched over a year ago, Bretta focuses on organic growth, creativity, and viral trends. The project is expanding strategically with future CEX listings, a merch line, and plans to enter the Asian market. It promotes a strong, loyal holder base and is designed to establish Bretta as a recognizable and lasting brand in the crypto space.
